1
00:00:11,190 --> 00:00:12,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for waiting.</font>

2
00:00:14,310 --> 00:00:17,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, my fave's doing a bunch
of shows on their national tour.</font>

3
00:00:18,380 --> 00:00:19,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh.</font>

4
00:00:19,170 --> 00:00:22,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't go to every show, but I want
to at least try to go to the ones nearby.</font>

5
00:00:23,480 --> 00:00:25,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. Are you listening?</font>

6
00:00:25,720 --> 00:00:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

7
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:29,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been answering me 
with simple responses.</font>

8
00:00:29,180 --> 00:00:32,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. Something's on my mind.</font>

9
00:00:33,470 --> 00:00:35,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm here for you if something's up.</font>

10
00:00:36,680 --> 00:00:40,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Recently, someone told me, 
"That's not fair." And...</font>

11
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:43,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were they right?</font>

12
00:00:44,290 --> 00:00:45,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think so, yeah.</font>

13
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't say anything back.</font>

14
00:00:49,050 --> 00:00:52,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been thinking about it since then, 
and I still can't find the answer.</font>

15
00:00:53,110 --> 00:00:55,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before I know it, 
I start thinking about it.</font>

16
00:00:55,700 --> 00:00:56,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

17
00:00:57,620 --> 00:00:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems like you've experienced it, too.</font>

18
00:01:00,370 --> 00:01:01,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The deeper you go into adulthood...</font>

19
00:01:01,890 --> 00:01:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter how much you fall in love,</font>

20
00:01:04,260 --> 00:01:06,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the feeling of sadness when you part</font>

21
00:01:07,970 --> 00:01:09,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or the pain when you hurt someone...</font>

22
00:01:10,060 --> 00:01:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It gets harder to find 
an answer for them.</font>

23
00:01:13,220 --> 00:01:15,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you look so troubled?</font>

24
00:01:15,470 --> 00:01:16,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

25
00:01:18,220 --> 00:01:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! Looks yummy!</font>

26
00:01:20,710 --> 00:01:23,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Margherita pizza with extra tomatoes.</font>

27
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:25,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that something off-menu?</font>

28
00:01:25,860 --> 00:01:28,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. A special service.</font>

29
00:01:29,040 --> 00:01:31,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You remind me more of Hoshikawa-sensei.</font>

30
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:32,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh.</font>

31
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, enjoy your meal.</font>

32
00:01:35,870 --> 00:01:38,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. By the way, Mizuho.</font>

33
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:39,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm?</font>

34
00:01:39,410 --> 00:01:41,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you free this weekend?</font>

35
00:03:25,930 --> 00:03:27,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for the wait, Mizuho.</font>

36
00:03:27,450 --> 00:03:28,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hop in.</font>

37
00:03:28,270 --> 00:03:31,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're taking your car? 
Are we going somewhere?</font>

38
00:03:31,270 --> 00:03:34,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. For a gourmet tour around Enoshima!</font>

39
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:38,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said you were working 
on new menu items.</font>

40
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you'd feed me 
a bunch of stuff at your restaurant.</font>

41
00:03:41,660 --> 00:03:45,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's important to try different foods 
when developing new menu items.</font>

42
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

43
00:03:47,420 --> 00:03:49,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. But what about the restaurant?</font>

44
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:53,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Big Bro's got it covered today.</font>

45
00:03:53,490 --> 00:03:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Togo!</font>

46
00:03:54,420 --> 00:03:56,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yo. It's been a while.</font>

47
00:03:56,880 --> 00:04:00,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have fun. You can leave things 
to your magnificent big bro.</font>

48
00:04:00,430 --> 00:04:02,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Togo!</font>

49
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:04,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should catch up sometime, too.</font>

50
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:05,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For sure.</font>

51
00:04:07,610 --> 00:04:09,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get going, Mizuho!</font>

52
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't seen him in a while, 
but I'm glad he seems to be doing fine.</font>

53
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:22,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. He's having fun as always.</font>

54
00:04:22,740 --> 00:04:25,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does he occasionally help out 
with the restaurant like that?</font>

55
00:04:25,340 --> 00:04:26,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

56
00:04:26,200 --> 00:04:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mostly on holidays and during busy seasons.</font>

57
00:04:29,420 --> 00:04:34,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His students and their families 
visit as customers, too.</font>

58
00:04:35,170 --> 00:04:36,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

59
00:04:36,060 --> 00:04:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not surprised Togo-sensei's so popular.</font>

60
00:04:39,220 --> 00:04:40,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

61
00:04:56,640 --> 00:05:00,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm thinking of dropping out of college 
and taking over the restaurant.</font>

62
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

63
00:05:01,860 --> 00:05:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So go back to being a teacher.</font>

64
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:08,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what this is about?</font>

65
00:05:08,870 --> 00:05:10,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about me.</font>

66
00:05:10,930 --> 00:05:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not attached to being a teacher.</font>

67
00:05:12,980 --> 00:05:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like what I'm doing 
with my current work.</font>

68
00:05:16,340 --> 00:05:19,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that there's anything 
I can't do in this world.</font>

69
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop hiding your true feelings like that.</font>

70
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You always try to carry 
the workload all by yourself.</font>

71
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just tell us.</font>

72
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:33,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are types of "love" 
that aren't spoken, you know.</font>

73
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose from your point of view</font>

74
00:05:39,110 --> 00:05:42,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it looks like I'm the only one 
shouldering everything.</font>

75
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:45,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this is something I decided on my own.</font>

76
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:49,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because family is important to me.</font>

77
00:05:49,690 --> 00:05:52,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this isn't something 
you should worry about.</font>

78
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I also decided this on my own.</font>

79
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:57,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm even licensed to be a chef now.</font>

80
00:05:59,790 --> 00:06:01,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not doing this for you.</font>

81
00:06:01,630 --> 00:06:03,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is something I want to do.</font>

82
00:06:05,890 --> 00:06:09,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I want you to do 
what you want to do, bro.</font>

83
00:06:09,700 --> 00:06:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go back to being a teacher.</font>

84
00:06:12,050 --> 00:06:14,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got me.</font>

85
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:17,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always thought I had to 
protect you. But now...</font>

86
00:06:19,970 --> 00:06:23,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before I knew it, 
you also became an adult.</font>

87
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I admit defeat.</font>

88
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

89
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:35,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh yeah.</font>

90
00:06:35,210 --> 00:06:38,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm leaving the 
welcome-back-to-work gifts to you.</font>

91
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:41,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe something like 
homemade Italian flan?</font>

92
00:06:41,210 --> 00:06:42,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why's it on me?</font>

93
00:06:43,410 --> 00:06:46,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you do this for your kind big bro?</font>

94
00:06:48,940 --> 00:06:50,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font color="#ffffff">Cut it out.</font></font>

95
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:21,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we want food we can walk 
around with, this is the place!</font>

96
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there anything you want, Syugo?</font>

97
00:07:23,450 --> 00:07:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah. Let's go to places 
you want to go.</font>

98
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:29,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we should get takoyaki first!</font>

99
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:31,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch out! Mizuho!</font>

100
00:07:32,490 --> 00:07:35,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful. You need to look ahead.</font>

101
00:07:35,730 --> 00:07:38,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, sorry. I'll be more careful.</font>

102
00:07:39,550 --> 00:07:40,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo?</font>

103
00:07:40,570 --> 00:07:44,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just thought that maybe we 
should keep holding hands like this.</font>

104
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:47,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm not a little kid.</font>

105
00:07:48,070 --> 00:07:49,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is embarrassing.</font>

106
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Takoyaki, right?</font>

107
00:07:51,990 --> 00:07:53,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C'mon. Let's go.</font>

108
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:55,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait up! Syugo!</font>

109
00:08:01,250 --> 00:08:03,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got nori on you, Mizuho.</font>

110
00:08:03,620 --> 00:08:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? No way!</font>

111
00:08:05,210 --> 00:08:06,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kidding!</font>

112
00:08:06,450 --> 00:08:07,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

113
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:09,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are viral on social media.</font>

114
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:12,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They are?</font>

115
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:14,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it tastes average, right?</font>

116
00:08:14,460 --> 00:08:16,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nuh-uh! They're delicious!</font>

117
00:08:24,420 --> 00:08:28,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you try making something 
that looks interesting, too?</font>

118
00:08:28,010 --> 00:08:29,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll think about it.</font>

119
00:08:33,810 --> 00:08:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So good!</font>

120
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:46,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We ate a lot.</font>

121
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's take a break.</font>

122
00:08:47,540 --> 00:08:48,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

123
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The breeze feels nice.</font>

124
00:09:01,030 --> 00:09:01,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

125
00:09:01,910 --> 00:09:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Look!</font>

126
00:09:03,610 --> 00:09:06,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There were hang gliders back then, too.</font>

127
00:09:07,050 --> 00:09:09,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love this view the most.</font>

128
00:09:09,820 --> 00:09:11,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you remember?</font>

129
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:12,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

130
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:18,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Back then... I remember 
wanting to be number one.</i></font>

131
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:22,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, guess you top-ranking guys 
wouldn't understand.</font>

132
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The real thrill of romance...</font>

133
00:09:25,830 --> 00:09:27,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is the bystander!</font>

134
00:09:29,300 --> 00:09:30,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understand?</font>

135
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:33,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what truly makes romance is...</font>

136
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:35,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">one-sided love!</font>

137
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo?</font>

138
00:09:39,890 --> 00:09:42,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, nothing.</font>

139
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's hit up the next place.</font>

140
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:44,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's next?</font>

141
00:09:44,740 --> 00:09:46,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The aquarium.</font>

142
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:49,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay! I haven't been there in a while!</font>

143
00:09:49,830 --> 00:09:53,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We saw the dolphin show 
last time with everyone.</font>

144
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:55,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, today it's just you and me.</font>

145
00:09:55,160 --> 00:09:56,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hm? Yeah!</font>

146
00:09:58,110 --> 00:10:01,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me. Can you take a photo of us?</font>

147
00:10:01,370 --> 00:10:04,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to join our picture 
while you're at it?</font>

148
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, but I'm with someone important.</font>

149
00:10:08,380 --> 00:10:10,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, Mizuho.</font>

150
00:10:19,340 --> 00:10:22,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I used to go up and down these steps
 effortlessly back in the day.</font>

151
00:10:23,550 --> 00:10:25,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to work out more. Here.</font>

152
00:10:27,180 --> 00:10:29,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Today... Syugo's acting a bit...</i></font>

153
00:10:29,650 --> 00:10:31,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, you're right.</font>

154
00:10:31,270 --> 00:10:34,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've changed from when 
we were younger, Mizuho.</font>

155
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:35,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've gotten prettier.</font>

156
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:37,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Careful!</font>

157
00:10:37,410 --> 00:10:38,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You okay?</font>

158
00:10:41,470 --> 00:10:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, I think I've done it now.</font>

159
00:10:43,790 --> 00:10:45,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you twist it?</font>

160
00:10:46,170 --> 00:10:49,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad. I forgot 
that you're wearing heels.</font>

161
00:10:49,140 --> 00:10:51,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must have been exhausted 
from all that walking.</font>

162
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:54,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not... It's not your fault.</font>

163
00:10:54,810 --> 00:10:56,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay still.</font>

164
00:10:57,220 --> 00:10:59,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa! Syugo!</font>

165
00:10:59,220 --> 00:11:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you move, you'll fall.</font>

166
00:11:01,890 --> 00:11:03,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put me down!</font>

167
00:11:03,450 --> 00:11:04,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can walk just fine!</font>

168
00:11:05,220 --> 00:11:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though you twisted your ankle 
and are wearing heels?</font>

169
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! Look!</font>

170
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:11,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like a drama!</font>

171
00:11:11,090 --> 00:11:13,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dang! He's so cool!</font>

172
00:11:14,030 --> 00:11:15,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The car's not far.</font>

173
00:11:15,830 --> 00:11:17,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can go to the aquarium some other day.</font>

174
00:11:17,950 --> 00:11:19,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go home for today.</font>

175
00:11:20,220 --> 00:11:22,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll... be in your care...</font>

176
00:11:30,390 --> 00:11:32,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Syugo.</font>

177
00:11:32,150 --> 00:11:33,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want me to take you to the hospital?</font>

178
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:34,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

179
00:11:34,900 --> 00:11:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it'll calm down once 
I apply a compress to it.</font>

180
00:11:37,180 --> 00:11:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then let's tend to it at home.</font>

181
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:42,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can cook you something good 
while I'm at it.</font>

182
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something's off about him after all...</font>

183
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:04,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

184
00:12:05,180 --> 00:12:07,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me help.</font>

185
00:12:07,180 --> 00:12:09,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you to stay put.</font>

186
00:12:09,580 --> 00:12:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The pain's not so bad 
since you treated me.</font>

187
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:17,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you're on soup duty.</font>

188
00:12:17,220 --> 00:12:18,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Roger!</font>

189
00:12:24,830 --> 00:12:25,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna taste test?</font>

190
00:12:28,950 --> 00:12:30,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good.</font>

191
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:31,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

192
00:12:31,580 --> 00:12:34,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one who made it, 
so of course it is.</font>

193
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:40,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your meals are really something special.</font>

194
00:12:40,150 --> 00:12:43,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, the pizza we had 
in Enoshima today was great,</font>

195
00:12:43,140 --> 00:12:46,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but your pizzas are still the best.</font>

196
00:12:48,550 --> 00:12:52,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you like them that much, 
want me to feed them to you every day?</font>

197
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:53,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd do that?</font>

198
00:12:53,230 --> 00:12:54,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd be the happiest girl.</font>

199
00:12:54,750 --> 00:12:56,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

200
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:59,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can make you happy.</i></font>

201
00:13:20,230 --> 00:13:24,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could have made dessert 
if we had more time.</font>

202
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:27,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just happy I got to
 eat your delicious food.</font>

203
00:13:27,580 --> 00:13:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time, I'll make you 
a special full course meal.</font>

204
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:31,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

205
00:13:31,700 --> 00:13:33,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the greatest, Syugo-sama!</font>

206
00:13:33,210 --> 00:13:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's me.</font>

207
00:13:34,310 --> 00:13:39,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The most generous and humorous 
chef of all time: Syugo-sama!</font>

208
00:13:39,590 --> 00:13:41,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't say all of that.</font>

209
00:13:41,410 --> 00:13:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think that the current me 
is more like the main lead</font>

210
00:13:46,250 --> 00:13:48,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">instead of a bystander?</font>

211
00:13:52,910 --> 00:13:54,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this about being a bystander?</font>

212
00:13:56,050 --> 00:13:57,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is yummy.</font>

213
00:13:57,650 --> 00:14:00,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything you touch 
turns delicious, Syugo.</font>

214
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that supposed to 
mean, Mizuho? Huh?</font>

215
00:14:04,330 --> 00:14:05,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. This?</font>

216
00:14:07,950 --> 00:14:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The manga writer 
I'm in charge of right now is...</font>

217
00:14:11,130 --> 00:14:13,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She just uploaded the draft.</font>

218
00:14:14,660 --> 00:14:16,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take a look.</font>

219
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font face="Arial"><font size="20"><font color="#9e9997">You can definitely do it!</font></font></font></font>

220
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial"><font size="20"><font color="#9e9997">You're gonna win today!</font></font></font></font>

221
00:14:18,920 --> 00:14:22,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This setting. It's the 
Mitsuman Swimming School.</font>

222
00:14:22,950 --> 00:14:25,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That takes me back.</font>

223
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

224
00:14:26,010 --> 00:14:30,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font face="Arial"><font size="20"><font color="#9e9997">You can definitely do it!</font></font></font></font>

225
00:14:26,010 --> 00:14:30,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial"><font size="20"><font color="#9e9997">You're gonna win today!</font></font></font></font>

226
00:14:26,410 --> 00:14:30,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I joined the writer there 
for an interview the other day.</font>

227
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:32,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

228
00:14:32,920 --> 00:14:34,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki?</font>

229
00:14:36,070 --> 00:14:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Turns out that the interviewee was Kizuki.</font>

230
00:14:39,290 --> 00:14:42,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She took a few photos for reference.</font>

231
00:14:44,760 --> 00:14:47,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How was he?</font>

232
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was super lively.</font>

233
00:14:50,010 --> 00:14:52,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Almost blinding.</font>

234
00:14:52,820 --> 00:14:57,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I felt like I'd been transported back to 
our high school days just looking at him.</font>

235
00:15:05,670 --> 00:15:10,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even in the future, Kizuki's 
always gonna be on Mizuho's mind...</i></font>

236
00:15:11,070 --> 00:15:12,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How nostalgic.</font>

237
00:15:15,890 --> 00:15:19,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then, every day was shimmering...</font>

238
00:15:23,230 --> 00:15:26,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure those days 
were my adolescence...</font>

239
00:15:26,900 --> 00:15:28,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to tell her.</i></font>

240
00:15:28,520 --> 00:15:30,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Something I've been meaning to say.</i></font>

241
00:15:33,040 --> 00:15:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Mizuho—</font>

242
00:15:33,040 --> 00:15:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was able to think about 
how I don't want to lose, either.</font>

243
00:15:42,650 --> 00:15:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're right. I also don't want to lose.</i></font>

244
00:15:46,530 --> 00:15:49,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to be the one closest to Mizuho.</i></font>

245
00:15:49,010 --> 00:15:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to be her number one.</i></font>

246
00:15:51,460 --> 00:15:52,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho.</font>

247
00:15:52,420 --> 00:15:56,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's something I've been meaning 
to say to you for a while now.</font>

248
00:15:56,360 --> 00:15:57,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Syugo?</font>

249
00:15:58,310 --> 00:16:02,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if Kizuki's all she sees...</i></font>

250
00:16:02,610 --> 00:16:05,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even if this is something 
that would bother her...</i></font>

251
00:16:05,690 --> 00:16:07,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho. Will you...</font>

252
00:16:08,700 --> 00:16:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. I think it's my dad.</font>

253
00:16:11,450 --> 00:16:12,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your dad?</font>

254
00:16:12,880 --> 00:16:14,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is he in Tokyo right now?</font>

255
00:16:14,410 --> 00:16:15,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

256
00:16:16,710 --> 00:16:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki?</font>

257
00:16:18,710 --> 00:16:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why's Kizuki here?</font>

258
00:16:20,510 --> 00:16:22,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I don't know.</font>

259
00:16:23,900 --> 00:16:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for showing up suddenly, Mizuho.</font>

260
00:16:26,810 --> 00:16:28,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

261
00:16:28,130 --> 00:16:29,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You see...</font>

262
00:16:31,460 --> 00:16:33,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why's Syugo here?</font>

263
00:16:33,720 --> 00:16:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's my line.</font>

264
00:16:35,560 --> 00:16:37,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold on, you two.</font>

265
00:16:37,870 --> 00:16:39,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So? Did you need something?</font>

266
00:16:39,730 --> 00:16:40,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

267
00:16:40,980 --> 00:16:43,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I'd stop by before practice.</font>

268
00:16:43,970 --> 00:16:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to tell you something, Mizuho.</font>

269
00:16:45,980 --> 00:16:46,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki!</font>

270
00:16:48,130 --> 00:16:51,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna be in a competition.</font>

271
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

272
00:16:52,680 --> 00:16:54,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations, Kizuki!</font>

273
00:16:54,370 --> 00:16:56,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

274
00:16:56,060 --> 00:16:58,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to tell you directly, Mizuho.</font>

275
00:16:58,830 --> 00:17:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I also wanted to see your face.</font>

276
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see... You'll be able to compete.</font>

277
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:06,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm rooting for you, too.</font>

278
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do your best, Kizuki.</font>

279
00:17:11,380 --> 00:17:14,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing with Syugo, Mizuho?</font>

280
00:17:14,690 --> 00:17:16,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Um...</font>

281
00:17:16,780 --> 00:17:21,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We went on a date around Enoshima, 
made dinner together,</font>

282
00:17:21,090 --> 00:17:23,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and now it's our post-meal coffee break.</font>

283
00:17:23,590 --> 00:17:25,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right? Mizuho?</font>

284
00:17:25,220 --> 00:17:27,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh.</font>

285
00:17:27,460 --> 00:17:30,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I'll even spend the night 
with her while I'm at it.</font>

286
00:17:30,280 --> 00:17:31,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

287
00:17:31,280 --> 00:17:32,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on!</font>

288
00:17:32,170 --> 00:17:34,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's just spouting his usual jokes!</font>

289
00:17:34,830 --> 00:17:36,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This might be my work calling.</font>

290
00:17:36,760 --> 00:17:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, I'm going to go check.</font>

291
00:17:52,050 --> 00:17:54,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#705136">Nishino</font></font>

292
00:17:55,880 --> 00:17:57,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

293
00:17:57,650 --> 00:17:59,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going home.</font>

294
00:17:59,140 --> 00:18:00,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, okay.</font>

295
00:18:01,560 --> 00:18:04,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. I almost forgot.</font>

296
00:18:04,090 --> 00:18:05,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love you, Mizuho!</font>

297
00:18:11,630 --> 00:18:15,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He always does as he pleases.</font>

298
00:18:22,680 --> 00:18:26,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For real. What do we do with him?</font>

299
00:18:27,340 --> 00:18:29,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He always acts impulsively</font>

300
00:18:29,490 --> 00:18:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and does whatever he pleases.</font>

301
00:18:33,620 --> 00:18:35,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, Syugo.</font>

302
00:18:35,090 --> 00:18:37,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were about to say something before.</font>

303
00:18:37,360 --> 00:18:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you want to say?</font>

304
00:18:40,930 --> 00:18:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuho. I...</font>

305
00:18:44,600 --> 00:18:45,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to tell her.</i></font>

306
00:18:45,900 --> 00:18:49,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't ever want to let Mizuho go.</i></font>

307
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:02,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

308
00:19:05,370 --> 00:19:06,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

309
00:19:06,620 --> 00:19:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to keep smiling.</font>

310
00:19:09,710 --> 00:19:12,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to be happy.</font>

311
00:19:12,270 --> 00:19:13,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

312
00:19:13,130 --> 00:19:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up with you, Syugo?</font>

313
00:19:17,490 --> 00:19:19,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

314
00:19:19,990 --> 00:19:22,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't it common sense to be nice 
to my childhood friend</font>

315
00:19:22,630 --> 00:19:25,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who tagged along with me 
for work research?</font>

316
00:19:27,480 --> 00:19:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were a big help today. Thanks.</font>

317
00:19:31,100 --> 00:19:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I also had a lot of fun.</font>

318
00:19:34,120 --> 00:19:35,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do it again sometime.</font>

319
00:19:38,180 --> 00:19:40,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong? Did you forget something?</font>

320
00:19:40,910 --> 00:19:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no. It's nothing.</font>

321
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:45,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful with your leg.</font>

322
00:19:45,610 --> 00:19:46,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Later.</font>

323
00:19:47,420 --> 00:19:49,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. See you.</font>

324
00:20:02,300 --> 00:20:03,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kizuki...</font>

325
00:20:04,740 --> 00:20:07,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's always straightforward 
about his feelings</font>

326
00:20:07,590 --> 00:20:10,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and hogs Mizuho all to himself.</font>

327
00:20:19,830 --> 00:20:21,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Mizuho.</font>

328
00:20:21,570 --> 00:20:24,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't let this one thing go.</font>

329
00:20:24,450 --> 00:20:28,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'll end these feelings.</font>

330
00:20:39,970 --> 00:20:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next up is this song:</i></font>

331
00:20:43,500 --> 00:20:48,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"My Regretful Heart."</i></font>

332
00:20:52,110 --> 00:20:53,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shiraishi-chan.</font>

333
00:20:53,570 --> 00:20:58,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I put up my courage but get rejected, 
would you comfort me?</font>

334
00:21:00,860 --> 00:21:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

335
00:21:02,380 --> 00:21:03,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

336
00:21:04,010 --> 00:21:05,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll play this song for you.</font>

337
00:21:27,290 --> 00:21:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He'll definitely regret it 
when he's older.</i></font>

338
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:32,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

339
00:21:33,450 --> 00:21:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't regret anything at all.</font>

340
00:23:34,810 --> 00:23:37,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello? This is Nishino.</font>

341
00:23:37,050 --> 00:23:39,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is the To-Ou Medical 
University Hospital.</i></font>

342
00:23:39,020 --> 00:23:42,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Your family member, Tsuyoshi 
Nishino-san has been hospitalized.</i></font>

343
00:23:42,320 --> 00:23:43,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

344
00:23:44,070 --> 00:23:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's currently being examined 
and treated here at the hospital.</i></font>

345
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:50,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But we're calling you to ask that 
a family member can come to the hospital</i></font>

346
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:54,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so we can explain the patient's condition 
and discuss future treatment options.</i></font>

347
00:23:54,580 --> 00:23:59,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font color="#d59199">Emergency Entrance</font></font>

348
00:24:02,000 --> 00:24:03,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nishino-san!</font>

349
00:24:03,460 --> 00:24:06,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sir! Can you hear me?</font>

350
00:24:10,010 --> 00:24:15,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font size="14"><font face="Arial"><font color="#1b1e1a"># 23 The Proposal</font></font></font></font>

